text: Kathleen Quinlan (born November 19, 1954 in Pasadena, California) is an American movie and television performer. She began her acting career with American Graffiti. She also did many television movies in the 1990s and 2000s. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Pasadena, California Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:American television actors
